nect is the official UNT email service for students and applicants. Do not risk missing official communication from the university. Students and applicants to the university regularly should check their EagleConnect email to view important communications from the following university offices. Office of the Registrar Financial Aid Student Accounting and other business services College, school, and departmental advisors Professors and classmates Library Notices Email Forwarding If you would like your email forwarded to an external address, such as Gmail, Yahoo, etc., you must configure forwarding in EagleConnect. Sign in to EagleConnect Is this your first time using EagleConnect? Please see these instructions if you need help! Need help logging in? EagleConnect HelpFrequently Asked Questions Need help installing Microsoft® Office?Install Microsoft© Office 365 on Desktop and MobileAccess your OneDrive account and Office Web Apps Sign-in correctly: Please ensure that you are signing in with your full email address. If you are having trouble logging in, please go to the EagleConnect Help page. Office 365 ProPlus now available to current students through EagleConnect: Current student EagleConnect accounts are now licensed to use Office 365 ProPlus! What comes with Office 365 ProPlus? Office 2013 for Windows 7, Windows 8(.1), and Windows 10 Office 2011 for Mac OSX 10.5.8 and newer Office Mobile for iOS 6.1 and newer (iPhone only) Office Mobile for Android 4.0 and newer These are full "offline" installations of Microsoft® Office. You will be able to use Office on up to five Windows or Mac machines and use Office Mobile on up to five mobile devices.  EagleConnect OneDrive and Office Web Apps Added Nov. 19, 2013: OneDrive and Office Web Apps were added to current student EagleConnect accounts. OneDrive offers 50GB of cloud based storage and Office Web Apps provide a free browser based version of the Microsoft Office suite. Oct. 29, 2013: EagleConnect email was upgraded to Microsoft® Office 365 Wave 15. UNT upgraded to Office 365 wave 14, the move to wave 15 added a number of features including an improved user interface, OneDrive and Office Web Apps. Watch an overview of the new EagleConnect Wave 15 features! Please visit the upgrade page to find out more information about the upgrade and answers to common questions. Please participate in the Help Desk Client Feedback Survey. Visit Us Sage Hall 1167 Union Circle Room 336 Denton, TX 76203 Mail Us 1155 Union Circle #310709 Denton, TX 76203-5017 Contact Us Main: 940-369-6029 | Help Desk: 940-565-2324 | Testing Center: 940-369-8665 unt.UIT@unt.edu; HelpDesk@unt.edu Technical issues? Site last updated on May 09, 2017 Disclaimer| AA/EOE/ADA| Privacy| Electronic Accessibility| State of Texas Online| Emergency Preparedness| THECB Online Resume System Student Consumer Information| UNT Compliance Hotline| Governors Committee on People with Disabilities| Texas Veterans Portal| UNT Home Site last updated on May 09, 2017 | Important Links 